data.description: Welcome to 6001 Psalmond Road! This charming brick home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, & natural beauty. Situated on a spacious 2-acre lot, there's ample space for relaxation. The house features 4 bedrooms & 4 bathrooms, ensuring plenty of room. With its split floor plan, privacy is assured, making it ideal for those seeking a peaceful retreat. The newly renovated kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting modern appliances & stylish finishes. Step outside and discover the true beauty of this property. The fenced-in yard provides a safe space to play freely. The newly installed saltwater pool offers a refreshing oasis on hot summer days, perfect for entertaining. The two-car rear garage provides convenient parking with a huge storage closet. This home also includes a 731 sqft basement with full bath, offering additional space for potential expansion. Great location with the best of both worlds - tranquility and convenience. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
